markets.title: Will VIctor Ponta win the 2024 Romanian presidential election?
markets.rules_primary: If Victor Ponta wins the next Romanian presidential election, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Clarification 10:30 AM ET 12/6/24: This morning, it was reported that the upcoming Romanian election was cancelled and the election process will restart. This market will remain open and will apply to the next Romanian presidential election, even if that election is delayed past 2024.
markets.early_close_condition: The market will close and expire following reporting that an individual has won the next Romanian presidential election.
